457
00:20:28,839 --> 00:20:29,400
Er Ye

458
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:30,720
Brother

459
00:20:31,119 --> 00:20:31,799
You pick.

460
00:20:34,839 --> 00:20:36,039
I'll just call you Brother then.

461
00:20:38,559 --> 00:20:39,039
That's fine.

462
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:40,359
Brother Deyuan

463
00:21:02,440 --> 00:21:03,000
You head back.

464
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:04,880
